<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="3.5.1">Jekyll</generator><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2017-08-07T09:55:47+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/</id><title type="html">파이썬으로 말해요 - PYCON Young Coder Tutorial</title><subtitle>파이콘코리아 2017</subtitle><author><name>Barbara Shaurette, Katie Cunningham</name></author><entry><title type="html">반복문</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/59/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="반복문" /><published>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/59</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/59/">&lt;div id=&quot;ppt&quot;&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;조건 루프&lt;/code&gt;는 무언가가 발생할 때까지 (또는 어떤 조건이 참일 때까지) 반복됩니다.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;div class=&quot;language-python summary highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;The count is:&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;count&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;The count is: 0
The count is: 1
The count is: 2
The count is: 3
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;while 키워드는 이러한 종류의 루프를 만드는 데 사용되며,
그래서 보통은 while 루프라고 부릅니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;desc&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h1 id=&quot;section&quot;&gt;반복문&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;반복문을 통과 할 때마다 카운터가 어떻게 증가하는지 설명해 보세요.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;무한 루프에 대해 얘기해보세요.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Barbara Shaurette, Katie Cunningham</name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">반복문</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/58/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="반복문" /><published>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/58</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/58/">&lt;div id=&quot;ppt&quot;&gt;
  &lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;계산 루프는 특정 횟수만큼 반복됩니다.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;계산이 끝날 때까지 계속 반복됩니다.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;/ul&gt;

  &lt;div class=&quot;language-python summary highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;mynum&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ow&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;]:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Hello&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;mynum&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Hello 1
Hello 2
Hello 3
Hello 4
Hello 5
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;for 키워드는 이런 종류의 루프를 만드는 데 사용되므로 대개 for 루프라고 합니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;desc&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h1 id=&quot;section&quot;&gt;반복문&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;리스트의 특정 부분에서 “for”문을 중지해 보세요.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Barbara Shaurette, Katie Cunningham</name></author><summary type="html">계산 루프는 특정 횟수만큼 반복됩니다. 계산이 끝날 때까지 계속 반복됩니다.</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">반복문</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/57/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="반복문" /><published>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/57</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/57/">&lt;div id=&quot;ppt&quot;&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;루프는 반복 작업을 하는 코드입니다.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;★ 계산 루프는 특정 횟수만큼 반복됩니다.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;★ 조건 루프는 특정 조건에 만족하거나 일부 조건이 참일 때까지 반복됩니다.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://i.imgur.com/Lp1C1eo.png&quot; alt=&quot;Loops&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Barbara Shaurette, Katie Cunningham</name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">if 구문</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/55/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="if 구문" /><published>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/55</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/55/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;ifelifelse-연습&quot;&gt;if/elif/else 연습&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;ppt&quot; class=&quot;summary&quot;&gt;

  &lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;color라는 변수가 “yellow”와 같은 경우 “Yay!”를 출력하는 if 문을 작성하세요.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;변수의 다른 값에 대해 두 개의 다른 메시지를 출력하려면 elif 절과 else 절을 추가하세요.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;/ul&gt;

  &lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;color&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;blue&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;color&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;yellow&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Yay!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;elif&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;color&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;purple&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Try again!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
       &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;We want yellow!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Barbara Shaurette, Katie Cunningham</name></author><summary type="html">if/elif/else 연습</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">if 구문</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/54/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="if 구문" /><published>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/54</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/54/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;ifelifelse-연습&quot;&gt;if/elif/else 연습&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;ppt&quot; class=&quot;summary&quot;&gt;

  &lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;color라는 변수가 “yellow”와 같은 경우 “Yay!”를 출력하는 if 문을 작성하세요.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;변수의 다른 값에 대해 두 개의 다른 메시지를 출력하려면 elif 절과 else 절을 추가하세요.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;/ul&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;(이제, 마지막 예제입니다.)&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Katie&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Katie&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Hi Katie!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
   &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;elif&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Barbara&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Hi Barbara!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
   &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Who are you?&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Barbara Shaurette, Katie Cunningham</name></author><summary type="html">if/elif/else 연습</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">if 구문</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/53/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="if 구문" /><published>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/53</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/53/">&lt;div id=&quot;ppt&quot;&gt;
  &lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;다양한 선택사항 추가:&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;/ul&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;If&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 민트아이스크림이 있고, 스쿱이 있어요.&lt;br /&gt;
    Or &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;else&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 바닐라가 있으면 2개를 먹을래요!&lt;br /&gt;
    Or &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;else&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 초콜릿이 있다면 3개를 주세요!&lt;br /&gt;
    Or 아니면 그냥 도넛을 먹을래요.”&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;elif 절을 사용하여 코드에 더 많은 선택 사항 추가 :&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;/ul&gt;

  &lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Katie&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Hi Katie!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
   &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;elif&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Barbara&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Hi Barbara!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
   &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Who are you?&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;desc&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h1 id=&quot;if-&quot;&gt;if 구문&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;여러 가지 옵션을 선택할 수 있게 하려면 어떻게 해야 할까요?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Barbara Shaurette, Katie Cunningham</name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">if 구문</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/52/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="if 구문" /><published>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/52</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/52/">&lt;div id=&quot;ppt&quot;&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;선택사항을 추가:&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;If&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 배가 고프면, 점심을 먹어요.&lt;br /&gt;
    Or &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;else&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 한 시간 안에 밥을 먹을 수 있습니다.”&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;If&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 민트아이스크림이 있다면, 스쿱을 가지고.&lt;br /&gt; 
    Or &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;else&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 바닐라를 떠 먹을 거에요.”&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;else 절을 사용하여 코드에 선택 항목 추가하기 :&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Katie&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Hi Katie!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;사기꾼!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;desc&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h1 id=&quot;if-&quot;&gt;if 구문&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;자, 이제 선택을 추가해 보세요.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Barbara Shaurette, Katie Cunningham</name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">if 구문</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/51/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="if 구문" /><published>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/51</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/51/">&lt;p class=&quot;summary&quot;&gt;“if 구문”을 다루는 한 가지 방법을 따라가 봅니다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;ppt&quot;&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;결정이 필요할 때:&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;If&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 배가 고프면, 점심을 먹어요.”&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;If&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 휴지통이 꽉 찼으면, 비우러 가요.”&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;조건이 충족되었을 때, &lt;br /&gt;
행동을 취합니다:&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Katie&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Katie&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;Hi Katie!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Hi Katie!
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;실생활에서 사용할 수 있는 ‘if 구문’의 몇 가지 예와 코드를 어떻게 사용해야 하는지에 대한 예제입니다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;desc&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h1 id=&quot;if-&quot;&gt;if 구문&lt;/h1&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;들여쓰기를 설명해 보세요.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;Idle은 자동으로 들여쓰기해줍니다. 하지만, 대부분의 파이썬 인터프리터는 공백 4개의 들여쓰기가 필요합니다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Barbara Shaurette, Katie Cunningham</name></author><summary type="html">“if 구문”을 다루는 한 가지 방법을 따라가 봅니다.</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">로직</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/49/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="로직" /><published>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2017-08-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/49</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/49/">&lt;p&gt;로직에 관해 이야기할 때, 코드에서 다음에 해야 할 일에 대한 결정을 내리는 것을 이야기합니다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;If 구문과 반복문을 배울거에요.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content><author><name>Barbara Shaurette, Katie Cunningham</name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">축하합니다! 당신은 이제 파이써니스타에요!</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/90/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="축하합니다! 당신은 이제 파이써니스타에요!" /><published>2017-08-05T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2017-08-05T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/90</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/PYCONKR-YoungCoder/90/">&lt;p&gt;축하합니다! 당신은 이제 파이써니스타에요(Pythonista)!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;왜&lt;/strong&gt; 파이썬을 배워야 할까요?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;게임을 만들 수 있다.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;음악과 비디오영상을 편집할 수 있다.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;웹사이트를 만들 수 있다.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;여러분의 숙제를 해 줄 프로그램을 짤 수 있어요 ….&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;다른 아이디어 없나요?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;파이썬기초를 배웠습니다. 그리고  스스로프로그램 몇 개를 작성하기도 했습니다. 이제 어떤 새로운 프로그램을 작성해보고 싶나요?(이슬라이드는 시간이 남는다면 마지막 수업에서 토론하는시간에 사용하세요.)&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Barbara Shaurette, Katie Cunningham</name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry></feed>